_sText: Anyways, here is a new death run map with a bit mixed up style. It contains loads of different types of textures, but it might remember you guys of some sort of a factory. It has all type of traps, from crushers, gas, lasers, electric, brakes, etc. Here is some basic info: - Indoors - Outdoors - 3d skybox - Soundscape - 17+2 traps - 38CT spawns - 2T spawns - Afk killer Here is a map video, but it's non updated, so you might notice some changes in the actual game. > To install the map, put the new cstrike folder over your old one and over write. Hope you enjoy the map. Rating, commenting, advising is more then welcome! Enjoy! :D
